    "Name": "Abyss",
    "Details": "A 60-ton platform built entirely from Star League salvage, the Abyss pairs an ER PPC with twin Artemis-guided SRM 6 launchers and Medium Pulse Lasers for brutal close-range damage. A Guardian ECM suite lets pilots close distance unseen. Those who faced it in the field rarely reported seeing the mech twice before it vanished back into the noise.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Targeting - Short</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.08</color></b>",
